org.lenskit.data.entities

Class EntityCollectionBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lenskit.data.entities.EntityCollectionBuilder

  • public class EntityCollectionBuilder
extends Object

    Builder class for entity collections. These builders are destructive: their build() methods destroy the internal storage, so the builder is single-use.
